- 'Collections shine the brightest' refers to the highest total value of inventory;
- 'Grand treasury' refers to the ranking of players based on the total value of their inventory.

- 'Most valuable treasure chest' refers to the shop with the highest total value of items;
- 'Considering the average quantity of each item' means using the average quantity of items across all shops in the calculation;
